data.description: Gorgeous one story home in an extremely desirable gated community in the Northwest. This four bedroom home shows real pride of ownership and has upgrades galore including den, upgraded tile flooring, tankless water heater, water softener, granite counter tops, dual pantry, upgraded bath tub, ample storage throughout plus much much more. The curb appeal is noticed from the moment you arrive and includes fully landscaped front and rear yard, added side pavers, upgraded wrought iron gate and covered patio. No money was spared at the time of build as extra insulation was added to the walls for sound dampening and also the attic for added temperature control. Situated within close proximity to local shops, amenities and easy access to both the 215 freeway and US-95 this home is an absolute must see. NO SIDS OR LIDS !!
